title: Test_Outside_File
text: We have weekly virtual lab meetings via Google Meet. We also meet in project teams virtually and in-person. We set the agenda and have running notes via google docs for all meetings. In addition, we have informal meetings and occasionally have team happy hours at the RSMAS WetLab.
